title: Doppelganger Machine, The - Radio Sci Fi Drama
description:
1 x 60 mins

Sci Fi Drama / Thriller by James Follett.

Christmas 1933 and a bi-plane carrying mail from Paris to London is heading for Croydon Aerodrome, but becomes lost in fog. It finally locates a huge airfield at which to land - Heathrow...... and it is covered in huge jets. What is more, it is the west European hub of Nazi Europe. What is happening.......?
